Known Issues

This document tracks known incomplete features, bugs, and temporary limitations in the system.

AI agents must read this file before proposing fixes or architecture changes.

Items listed here are intentional known gaps and should not trigger architectural redesign.

Task System
Task Editing Modal Not Implemented

Clicking Edit Task currently shows a placeholder message:

