Today Board Does Not Display All Scheduled Tasks

Tasks scheduled in the Weekly Scheduler may not appear on the Today Board.

Likely cause:

The Today Board query does not yet include ad-hoc tasks created via the custom task flow.

This is a known integration gap.

AI tools should fix the query rather than redesigning the task system.

