Manager Notes Authorization
Admin Account Not Linked to Employee Record

When attempting to send manager notes, the system may display:

Your admin account is not linked to an employee record.

The UI provides a button to create the admin employee record.

Current issue:

The action fails due to a role check:

if (profile?.role !== 'admin') throw new Error("Unauthorized")

This is inconsistent with the capability-based permission system.

This should eventually be updated to use capability checks rather than raw role checks.

Scheduler UI
Drawer Interaction Was Recently Refactored

Scheduler cards now open a right-side drawer implemented via React Portal.

This prevents clipping issues caused by grid overflow.

If the drawer fails to appear, check:

portal mounting

z-index

event propagation

Do not redesign the scheduler layout unless necessary.

