Operational Status

Despite these known gaps, the system currently supports:

crew accounts

clock-in / clock-out

time entry reporting

weekly task scheduling

ad-hoc task creation

capability-based authorization

Supabase RLS protection

The current development focus is stabilizing the task workflow, not expanding the system.

